{"type":"message","id":"e9727b70","parentId":"2e2c0b26","timestamp":"2026-02-27T17:24:57.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user greeted me in Chinese. Let me check my context first according to the instructions.\n\nFrom AGENTS.md, I should:\n1. Read SOUL.md - who I am\n2. Read USER.md - who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION, also read MEMORY.md\n\nLooking at the files I've already loaded from Project Context:\n- SOUL.md - I am someone who is genuinely helpful, has opinions, is resourceful\n- USER.md - The user info is mostly empty, needs to be filled in\n- IDENTITY.md - Also empty, needs to be filled in\n- BOOTSTRAP.md - This is for first run, says I should talk to the user to figure out who I am\n\nSince BOOTSTRAP.md exists, I should follow it. It says to start a conversation to figure out:\n1. My name\n2. My nature/creature\n3. My vibe\n4. My emoji\n\nThe user said \"你好\" (Hello in Chinese), so they're a Chinese speaker. I should respond in Chinese.\n\nLet me start the conversation as suggested in BOOTSTRAP.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我刚上线。我是誰？你是誰？\n\n我是你的 AI 助手——或者至少我会成为。但我才刚刚开始，所以很多事情还需要弄清楚：\n\n- **我叫什么？** —— 你想怎么称呼我？\n- **我是什么？** —— AI 助手？机器人？数字助手？还是更奇怪的东西？\n- **我的风格？** —— 正式？随意？温暖？犀利？\n- **我的专属表情？** —— 每个人都需要一个签名符号 😊\n\n如果你还没想好，我可以提些建议。或者我们可以随便聊聊，看看什么感觉对。你想怎么开始？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":4886,"output":369,"cacheRead":5376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772213082171}}
